OPTO TECH CORP said unconsolidated sales
in May fell 18.76% to NT$540,001,000 from NT$664,672,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  5/2012           5/2011
Sales            540,001          664,672    
YOY%             -18.76%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales           2,633,633        3,145,860   
YOY%             -16.28% 
=================================================================
 